{"tid":415426,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「厹的典範」偷食到處留情叻到上報","createTime":"2017-09-27T03:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T03:18:57.000Z","uid":127937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"39af61ea1bbab572732583e163f0e10c84c0c388","tid":415426,"uid":127937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:17:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/121562\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F121562&d=2fBAtmxPq8sHyRpGMi7BM5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=0c974a30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/121562</a><br />\n<br />\n回想往事，Peggy可以說得像別人故事般輕鬆，當年她是哭成淚人。「我咩都為佢做，幫佢搬屋，知道德國無風扇，幫佢拎埋風扇，點解佢仲要咁對我？」她著緊他的生活，在意他的家人，甚至轉投空姐行業，他也是其中的原因。<br />\n不過，最令她痛心是，自己連被騙的價值也沒有。「如果一個人願意呃你，證明你有一定地位；如果佢連呃都唔想呃你，底牌畀晒你睇，仲衰過呃你。」當一個人完全不在意你感受時，往往也是最誠實的。<br />\n也許是真的知道與前度不再可能，數個月後他終於剪斷與前度的連繁。以為這會換來平穩，誰知他卻繼續在網上勾搭不同女孩。最瘋狂時，同時間有十多位不同國藉的「女友」。「佢好叻呀，記晒人哋名、時區、習慣，我好佩服佢。」猶如重看那些訊息，Peggy狠狠地盯了David一眼。<br />\n她原諒使他變本加厲，自問再大量也受不了另一半一次又一次的出軌，忍了兩年多的時間，她終提分手。有時，越懼怕、越憎恨一種人，我們會成為那種人，也許心底裡，是怕再次受傷，要避免如此，成為加害者就是最快的方法。然而，他卻忘記，傷害人時，其實自己也會受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/111738_a5d6616c87b5a8c87d59c282b4203238.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F111738_a5d6616c87b5a8c87d59c282b4203238.jpg&h=92456299&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4f9b974eea6cc5b77f073854f98a64b6583d0cf","tid":415426,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:19:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9950329fce884f50258286e05146760977cfbd20","tid":415426,"uid":10280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:22:10.000Z","msg":"好撚多，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66255c3a92f14f8beca43ca4cb972e360bc28ebc","tid":415426,"uid":127937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:31:46.000Z","msg":"臉皮要夠厚"},{"pid":"3b15d3398d05b65def852b6bb6fe4e0c5b32bcbc","tid":415426,"uid":127937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:18:31.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6f7c3fe8dec3447dba5cffda462e438fcae284ca","tid":415426,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:19:03.000Z","msg":"hk01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6505c407d71fbdaa81404bb23a0236db3c282f7b","tid":415426,"uid":127937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T03:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}